actions.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Voice Vote.

official_title: A resolution to authorize testimony and the production of documents by Senate employees at an unemployment compensation hearing.

summary.text: Authorizes Kathleen M. Ramsey, Mary Harris, and any other Senate employee whose testimony may be necessary to testify and produce documents at unemployment compensation proceedings concerning Felix Lockett, pending before the District of Columbia Department of Employment Services.

titles.title: A resolution to authorize testimony and the production of documents by Senate employees at an unemployment compensation hearing.
